Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [Tanggal berlaku]

1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how wawancara.ai ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, discloses, and safeguards your information when you use our mobile application wawancara.ai (the "App"). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this Privacy Policy, please do not access the App.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect information about you in the following ways:

a. Personal Data

Personally identifiable information, such as your name, email address, and demographic information, that you voluntarily provide to us when you register with the App or engage with the App.

b. Data Collected Automatically

The App may automatically collect information about your device, including your IP address, operating system, browser type, and usage details when you interact with the App.

c. User-Provided Data

We may collect other information you provide to us directly, such as feedback or other communications.

3. Video Data Processing

When you use the App to upload videos, these videos are processed for the purpose of detection (such as facial recognition, motion tracking, etc.). wawancara.ai does not store your video files. Once the processing and detection tasks are completed, the video files are immediately deleted from our systems.

4. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide, operate, and maintain our App.
Process and analyze videos you upload for detection purposes.
Improve, personalize, and enhance your experience with the App.
Understand and analyze how you use our App to improve its functionality.
5. Disclosure of Your Information

We do not share or sell your personal information or processed video data to third parties. We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect the rights, property, or safety of wawancara.ai, our users, or others.

6. Data Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect the information we collect. However, please note that no data transmission over the internet or storage method can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Email Kontak Anda].
